<h2>What's New in 1.9.7</h2>  <ul><li><strong>More reliable widget updates</strong> — fixed cases where widgets could stay stuck on old values after an app update.</li> <li><strong>Refresh button behaves better</strong> — widget refreshes now recover more consistently instead of appearing to do nothing.</li> <li><strong>Smoother upgrades</strong> — the app repairs widget registration on launch so replacing or auto-updating the app is less likely to strand the widgets.</li></ul>
